desc_short	-----								"Planet R-12" is a 2D tactical shooter. Your squad of persistent soldiers accidently landed on a planet of robots, populated by hostile mechanisms and war machines. Each step on a planet is full of dangers and soldiers really need your skills and abilities.							
developer									Timushev Vladimir					,			Composer-Motorin Dmitry (Djinotan)								
